taducyate—cittādhīno dharmaḥ, dharmādhīnā bodhir iti.

<commentary>evaṃ cittāyattatāṃ sarvatra niścitya cittadṛḍhatāyām udāharaṇam āha.

asamāhitajanamadhye punar upaghātabhayāt tadgatamanasā yathā vraṇaṃ rakṣati kaścid apramattaḥ, evaṃ tathā śikṣārakṣaṇakāmaḥ akāraṇavairibālajanamadhye saṃvasan tatparaścittaṃ vraṇam iva rakṣet sarvakālam.</commentary>
